

# Get rooms
### Get all rooms
GET http://localhost:3333/rooms

### Create a room
POST http://localhost:3333/rooms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Room",
  "description": "A test room for testing activities"
}

### Get room by ID
GET http://localhost:3333/rooms/YOUR_ROOM_ID_HERE

### Create activity for a room
POST http://localhost:3333/rooms/YOUR_ROOM_ID_HERE/activities
Content-Type: application/json

### Get activities for a room
GET http://localhost:3333/rooms/YOUR_ROOM_ID_HERE/activities

### Get specific activity
GET http://localhost:3333/activities/YOUR_ACTIVITY_ID_HERE

### Submit activity response
POST http://localhost:3333/activities/YOUR_ACTIVITY_ID_HERE/submit
Content-Type: application/json

